@startuml
title Performance investigation
autonumber

participant "Playwright Spec" as Spec
participant "TickerInvestigationPage" as PageObject
participant "InvestigationEndpoints" as Api
participant "Browser CDP Session" as Cdp
participant "TickerTime App" as App
participant "window.__tickerMetrics" as Metrics

Spec -> PageObject: applyScenario(settings)
PageObject -> Api: POST /api/investigation/scenario
Api --> PageObject: 204 No Content

Spec -> PageObject: gotoPipe() / gotoSignal()
PageObject -> Cdp: Performance.enable
PageObject -> App: navigate(route)
App -> Metrics: reset()

Spec -> PageObject: subscribeFirst(count)
Spec -> PageObject: run live or scrub actions

loop during scenario
  App -> Metrics: record derivation and latency samples
end

Spec -> PageObject: readBenchmarkResult()
PageObject -> Metrics: flush()
Metrics --> PageObject: app metrics
PageObject -> Cdp: Performance.getMetrics
Cdp --> PageObject: cdp metrics
PageObject --> Spec: BenchmarkRunResult

@enduml
